== Overview ==
The Vulcan Cannon unleashes a hail of high velocity rounds causing significant damage to targets with light armor deflection. Like all [[:Category:Weapons (Light Armor Piercing)|LAP class weapons]] the Vulcan lacks shield penetrative power.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Vulcan Cannon can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
